author: NEW YORK DAILY NEWS
title: VIDEO: Buster Skrine lays out Julian Edelman with brutal hit
text:
JOHN CETRINO/EPA Buster Skrine handles Julian Edelman with extreme brutality. Buster Skrine may be small, but he packs a lot of punch.
The slot corner absolutely demolished Julian Edelman after the Patriots wide receiver caught a pass in the second quarter of the Jets-Patriots game. Just after Edelman caught the ball and turned around and was crushed by Skrine, who led with his shoulder. Edelman was de-cleated and leveled.
